[I] KDE Frameworks solution for user-configurable main windows

[T] KXMLGUI provides a framework for managing menu and toolbar actions in an
[T] abstract way. The actions are configured through a XML description and
[T] hooks in the application code.

[U] https://invent.kde.org/frameworks/kxmlgui

